{"id":232818731,"title":"A6400翻轉螢幕對焦AFC問題","content":"想問各位大大\nSony6400最火的就是它的連續對焦AFC超強\n但是最近我發現我買的6400拍照模式\n一翻轉螢幕之後沒有AFC只有AFS\n在翻轉螢幕的時候不免俗就是設定倒數計時\n先按快門再移到我要的位置等秒數到\n但是AFS會在我按下快門就對焦\n所以之後走到對的位置的時候就是失焦的狀態\n我是有想過 如果用手機操控相機可以解決這個問題\n但是如果我們偶爾只是想要拍一張3人自拍照\n不可能還在那邊手機操控\n那翻轉螢幕過後到底要怎麼樣才能對到焦呢\n因為手也沒這麼長 每一次都拿超遠按快門😭\n一定是先按了再手伸出去😰\n有人有遇到一樣的問題嗎 跪求解答😭\n\n未翻轉的對焦模式都能使用\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/a5245f88-7777-43cf-abf4-64b7a309929b/1280.jpeg\n翻轉之後只有 AFS AFA DMF MF\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7089fd68-f250-4b3a-859a-a747dd20fe19/1280.jpeg","excerpt":"想問各位大大，Sony6400最火的就是它的連續對焦AFC超強，但是最近我發現我買的6400拍照模式，一翻轉螢幕之後沒有AFC只有AFS，在翻轉螢幕的時候不免俗就是設定倒數計時，先按快門再移到我要的位","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d0cd5819-4627-4b5f-8a8e-050976e0fba1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-03T12:57:15.938Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-03T12:57:15.938Z","commentCount":3,"likeCount":4,"tags":[],"topics":["單眼","微單"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"攝影","forumAlias":"photography","school":"實踐大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":4}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/a5245f88-7777-43cf-abf4-64b7a309929b/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7089fd68-f250-4b3a-859a-a747dd20fe19/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c980e9b4-7df7-47bc-bf3e-0cbbdcd2cfb8","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/a5245f88-7777-43cf-abf4-64b7a309929b/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/a5245f88-7777-43cf-abf4-64b7a309929b/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/a5245f88-7777-43cf-abf4-64b7a309929b/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-03T12:57:15.93